{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_22c7e5a8728463a1e6277290", "problem_id": "prob_5da7cf98f55f46b28635a500", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "1", "normalized_question_text": "智能手机上装载的众多app软件改变着我们的生活。如图所示为百度地图app软件的一张截图,表示了某次导航的具体路径,其推荐路线中有两个数据,10min,5.4公里,关于这两个数据,下列说法正确的是( )\nA.研究汽车在导航图中的位置时,可以把汽车看作质点\nB.10min表示的是某个时刻\nC.5.4公里表示了此次行程的位移的大小\nD.根据这两个数据,我们可以算出此次行程的平均速度的大小", "normalized_answer_text": "A", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "open", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "good", "solvability_score": 1.0, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "pass", "decision_reason_codes": ["low_resolution", "meets_cleaning_requirements"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T21:53:27Z"}
