{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_065605c104ef1121ca649217", "problem_id": "prob_4dc9bded911b5be502adec2a", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "5", "normalized_question_text": "攀岩运动是一种考验人的意志与心理素质的运动形式,户外攀岩运动更加刺激与惊险。如图所示为一户外攀岩运动的场景与运动线路图,该攀岩爱好者从起点a到b,最终到达c,据此图判断下列说法中正确的是( )", "normalized_answer_text": "攀岩爱好者所走路程要比自起点到终点的位移大", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "bad", "solvability_score": 0.8, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "reject", "decision_reason_codes": ["alignment_status_bad", "implicit_visual_dependency", "low_alignment_consistency", "missing_grounded_visual_path", "no_reasoning_path", "text_image_misaligned"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T21:56:38Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_ffaa882632b66dff7d21a76c", "problem_id": "prob_29b1a07c69ffbe9373de67cf", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "6", "normalized_question_text": "结合图片中交代的情景及数据,以下判断正确的是( )", "normalized_answer_text": "高速行驶的磁悬浮列车的加速度可能为零\n轿车时速为100km/h,紧急刹车距离为31m(可视为匀减速至静止),由此可得轿车刹车阶段的加速度为$a{=}12.5\\mathrm{m/s}^{2}$\n根据图中数据可求出刘翔在110m栏比赛中通过全程的平均速率为$v=8.42\\mathrm{m/s}$", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "bad", "solvability_score": 0.8, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "reject", "decision_reason_codes": ["bad_alignment", "low_resolution", "low_text_completeness", "missing_grounded_visual_path", "normalized_question_incomplete", "severe_crop_loss", "text_image_misaligned"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T21:57:30Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_99dee6c52135e349073eb1ca", "problem_id": "prob_26ba3f0a605470ce17032f06", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "7", "normalized_question_text": "如图所示,气垫导轨上滑块经过光电门时,其上的遮光条将光遮住,电子计时器可自动记录遮光时间$\\Delta t$,测得遮光条的宽度为$\\Delta x$,用$\\frac{\\Delta x}{\\Delta t}$近似代表滑块通过光电门时的瞬时速度,为使$\\frac{\\Delta x}{\\Delta t}$更接近瞬时速度,正确的措施是( )", "normalized_answer_text": "换用宽度更窄的遮光条", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "bad", "solvability_score": 0.8, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "reject", "decision_reason_codes": ["bad_alignment", "implicit_visual_dependency", "missing_grounded_visual_path", "severe_crop_loss", "text_image_misaligned"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T21:58:18Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_4f38d93cafd589f8e5920977", "problem_id": "prob_76daf91e34f038403954e938", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "8", "normalized_question_text": "如图所示为甲、乙两质点做直线运动时,通过打点计时器记录的两条纸带,两纸带上各计数点间的时间间隔都相同.关于两质点的运动情况的描述,下列说法中正确的是( )", "normalized_answer_text": "两质点在$t_{0}\\sim t_{4}$时间内的平均速度相同\n两质点在$t_{2}$时刻的速度大小相等\n两质点不一定是从同一地点出发的,但在$t_{0}$时刻甲的速度为0", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "bad", "solvability_score": 0.8, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "reject", "decision_reason_codes": ["alignment_bad", "low_resolution", "missing_grounded_visual_path", "severe_crop_loss", "solvability_hint_reject", "text_image_misaligned", "visual_grounding_unavailable"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T21:59:27Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_098a3bb6d0cf579316399303", "problem_id": "prob_66a5208237e0ae3b16dc2653", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "9", "normalized_question_text": "如图所示为一个质点运动的位移x随时间t变化的图象,由此可知质点在0~4s内", "normalized_answer_text": "t=2s时速度一定最大\n速率为5m/s的时刻有两个", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "bad", "solvability_score": 0.8, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "reject", "decision_reason_codes": ["alignment_bad", "low_resolution", "low_text_completeness", "missing_grounded_visual_path", "normalized_question_incomplete", "severe_crop_loss", "text_image_misaligned"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T22:00:34Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_cdc2ea91746b77005583844b", "problem_id": "prob_9ac231b846f1124a2961b00b", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "10", "normalized_question_text": "如图所示是一做匀变速直线运动的质点的位置–时间图象(x–t图象),P(t1,x1)为图象上一点。PQ为过P点的切线,与x轴交于点Q(0,x2)。已知t=0时质点的速度大小为v0,则下列说法正确的是", "normalized_answer_text": "质点的加速度大小为$\\frac{x_{1}-x_{2}}{t_{1}^{2}}-\\frac{v_{0}}{t_{1}}$", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "good", "solvability_score": 1.0, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "pass", "decision_reason_codes": ["meets_cleaning_requirements"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T22:01:39Z"}
{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_a141ba9c8fca91fa4b00533f", "problem_id": "prob_8afe1577496db838653292e2", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "11", "normalized_question_text": "如图甲所示为速度传感器的工作示意图,P为发射超声波的固定小盒子,工作时P向被测物体发出短暂的超声波脉冲,脉冲被运动的物体反射后又被P接收。从P发射超声波开始计时,经时间△t再次发射超声波脉冲。图乙是两次发射的超声波的位移-时间图象,则下列说法正确的是", "normalized_answer_text": "物体在t1~t2时间内的平均速度为$\\frac{x_2-x_1}{t_2-t_1}$", "image_count": 2, "has_multiple_images": true, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "bad", "solvability_score": 0.8, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "reject", "decision_reason_codes": ["bad_alignment", "implicit_visual_dependency", "low_resolution", "missing_grounded_visual_path", "text_image_misaligned"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T22:02:23Z"}
