{"clean_problem_record_id": "cleanprob_1254520b26225f92232f9a73", "problem_id": "prob_bf39aaf2dd830cf48041e87f", "source_dataset": "Multi-Physics", "source_problem_id": "17", "normalized_question_text": "一质点沿一条直线运动,其位移随时间t的变化关系如图3所示,Oa段和cd段为直线、ac段为曲线,Oa段的平均速度为$v_{1}$,ac段的平均速度为$v_{2}$,cd段的平均速度为$v_{3}$,Od段平均速度为$v_{4}$,则", "normalized_answer_text": "$v_{1}$,$v_{2}$$v_{3}$和$v_{4}$中$v_{3}$最大\n在ac段一定存在一个时刻,此时刻的瞬时速度等于$v_{4}$", "image_count": 1, "has_multiple_images": false, "requires_image": true, "text_dominant": false, "cleaning_path": "multimodal_full", "question_type": "multiple_choice", "open_variant_count": 1, "alignment_status": "bad", "solvability_score": 0.8, "solvability_path_mode": "multimodal", "clean_decision": "reject", "decision_reason_codes": ["bad_alignment", "implicit_visual_dependency", "low_alignment_consistency", "missing_grounded_visual_path", "no_reasoning_path", "text_image_misaligned"], "created_at": "2026-03-27T22:07:41Z"}
